NEW FEATURES:

1/23/2017
* Prompt will now display MaxHit, MaxMana and MaxMove (if toggled)
* Prompt will optionally display enemy's condition (do 'prompt all' or 'prompt hmvc')
* Type 'help condition' to see how condition and HP percentage are correlated
* 'say' verb now displays in cyan when you use normal or complete color modes

1/24/2017
* 'score' enhanced to display stats, regen rates and other helpful info. Up for feedback
* worn containers can now be accessed directly ('put' and 'get' will work)
